      {
        "question": "Can food affect results? ",
        "answer": "Not significantly unless salt intake is extreme."
      },
      {
        "question": "Is the test painful? ",
        "answer": "Blood draw may cause mild discomfort."
      },
      {
        "question": "What happens if my levels are abnormal? ",
        "answer": "Your doctor will recommend further testing or treatment based on the likely cause."
      },
      {
        "question": "How long for results? ",
        "answer": "Typically, 24–48 hours at Cadabams Diagnostics."
      }
